full_summary:
# 21120-237185 Request for Proposal for Insoles
## Description
The Correctional Service of Canada (CSC) has a requirement for insoles for gym shoes. The purchase description is CAG-2-0505-764B.

### Quantities

- Firm quantities: 16,560 pairs for a period not specified.
- Requested quantities: 4,500 pairs for a period of 36 months from contract award.
- Option quantities: up to 45,000 pairs for a period of 36 months from contract award.

## Delivery
All deliverables are to be delivered to [Laval, Quebec](https://www.google.com/maps/search/Laval+Québec) after March 31, 2024.

## Tender Details
- **Reference Number**: WS4221537896
- **Solicitation Number**: WS4221537896
- **Publication Date**: 2023-09-22
- **Tender Closing Date**: 2023-11-24T14:00:00
- **Amendment Number**: 2
- **Amendment Date**: 2023-10-24
- **Expected Contract Start Date**: 2024-02-12
- **Expected Contract End Date**: 2026-11-19

## Contract Details
- **Procurement Category**: Goods and Services
- **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open
- **Selection Criteria**: Highest Combined Rating of Technical Merit and Price
- **Trade Agreements**: Various Free Trade Agreements (list provided)
- **Regions of Opportunity**: None
- **Regions of Delivery**: Laval, Quebec

## Contact Information
For further information, please contact:
Darya Kritova (SPAC/PSPC)
darya.kritova@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
